725696f-c.title: Queens: 86th Avenue - 111th Street
725696f-c.text:
86th Avenue (right), north side, from l11th to 112th
Streets, looking east and showing the Holy Child Jesus
Roman Catholic Church. View 3 shows the 112th Street side
of the church, and view 4 the parochial school on the south
side of 86th Avenue.
P. L. Sperr  May 7, 1934
